entries.arrived_at_loc: Good, you got there fast. Our smuggler should be there soon.
entries.attack_notify: Tactical Computer: < Incoming fighter vessels. Scans show weapons armed. >
entries.attack_stopped: Tactical Computer: < No more fighter vessels within sensor range. >
entries.complete: Awesome pilot, this should be the last thing we need to be able to get out of here. Return to your base on Yavin 4 for some rest.
entries.failed_destroy: Damn the Empire, we needed those supplies!
entries.failed_protect: Bah! The smuggler had to bail, he had too many enemies on him.
entries.found_loc: Rebel Fleet Command: < Meet the smuggler at these coordinates. >
entries.goodbye_1: Good show, I owe you one!
entries.goodbye_2: Good show, I owe you one!
entries.goodbye_3: Good show, I owe you one!
entries.goodbye_4: Good show, I owe you one!
entries.goodbye_5: Good show, I owe you one!
entries.hull_half: Cripes, my old baby is falling apart, I need help!
entries.panic_1: I guess it was too much to hope for a smooth ride.
entries.panic_2: No one said there would be more TIE fighters than asteroids here!
entries.panic_3: Prepare for a fight, incoming bad guys!
entries.panic_4: My ship is being scanned, they will attack when they see what I have on-board!
entries.panic_5: TIE-Fighters! They don't look too happy either.
entries.quest_escort_d: Escort the smuggler to our fleet. Try to avoid contact with Imperial forces at all costs and above all, don't lead any of them to our fleet! Good luck pilot.
entries.quest_location_d: It's our hope that you and the smuggler will be able to sneak past the Imperial presence in the system as they are looking for bigger targets but it will be hard since they seem to be all over now.
entries.quest_rendezvous_d: You have been supplied with the coordinates of where the smuggler will meet with you. Make haste to this location.
entries.reason_1: Good to see you, lets get this stuff to the fleet.
entries.reason_2: Good to see you, lets get this stuff to the fleet.
entries.reason_3: Good to see you, lets get this stuff to the fleet.
entries.reason_4: Good to see you, lets get this stuff to the fleet.
entries.reason_5: Good to see you, lets get this stuff to the fleet.
entries.shields_depleted: My shields are failing! I'm taking some serious damage here!
entries.taunt_1: You will never deliver that stuff Rebel!
entries.taunt_4: You will fall from the might of the Empire!
entries.taunt_5: What will this Rebel kill bring me to today guys? 5?
entries.thanks_2: Well we showed them didn't we?
entries.thanks_5: You're lucky I'm here, did you see me blast that TIE? It was beautiful!
entries.title: Endor system: Escort smuggler to fleet.
entries.title_d: One of our smugglers has arrived with the materials necessary to repair the hyperdrive systems on our capital ships. He needs an escort but we don't want to attract too much attention so you will assist him by yourself.
